snippet.title: Super Buckyball Tournament Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Buckyball Tournament (SBT), our brand new multiplayer ball game that will hit early access in 2019. 

Follow us on discord to play the alpha test this summer!

Website: https://superbuckyball.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/Bh8tTbD
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperBuckyBall 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperBuckyballtournament
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/superbuckyballtournament
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperBuckyballTourney
